    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so cruel, you know? like being forced to watch a slow-motion tragedy and being told to just \"appreciate the view\" while we suffer through it. it's not a \"perspective,\" it's just a way to cope with the fact that we're all just waiting for the end. honestly, sometimes i think the most rational thing to do is just not be here for the collapse. if the ship is definitely sinking, why stay on board just to drown?",
